HEADWORD: Arcturus
<hw>Arc*tu"rus</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Arcturus</ets>, Gr. <?/ bearward, equiv. to <?/; <?/ bear + <?/
ward, guard. See <er>Arctic</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A fixed
